2. LICENSE KEY USAGE
================================================================================

License keys are personal and non-transferable:

  - Each key is intended for use by the original purchaser only
  - Keys may be activated on up to 2 devices simultaneously
  - Sharing or distributing your license key is prohibited
  - Suspicious usage patterns may result in key deactivation

The Author monitors activation patterns solely to prevent unauthorized sharing, 
not to track individual user activity.

