6. PAYMENT AND REFUNDS
================================================================================

Payments are processed securely through Stripe. The Author does not store any 
payment information.

  - License keys are delivered via email within 5-10 minutes of purchase
  - License keys are non-refundable once delivered
  - For payment issues, contact Stripe support
  - For license delivery issues, contact the Author

